   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Year two of Imperator Caesar Nerva Trajanus Augustus Germanicus. Has performed for five days for work on dikes for the same second year on the new dyke of the canal, (2nd h.) on behalf of Tebtunis, Herakles son of Horos the son of Herakles, his mother is Tenapeis. (3rd h.) I, Maron, katasporeus, have signed. (4th h.) I, Eudaimon, antigrapheus of (the office of) the strategos, have signed. (5th h.) I, Aphrodeitos, have signed.</ab>
         </div>
